description:
PDF Watermark App by Algoworks is a highly useful PDF document watermarking tool built for businesses and users that would like to prevent copyright infringement and plagiarism across the Salesforce platform. A watermark is a faded background image or text that displays behind the text in a document. You can use them to indicate a document's state (confidential, draft, etc.), add a subtle company logo, or even for a bit of artistic flair.

With our quick, efficient app, users can now add watermark in their PDF documents through click of a button from inside Salesforce. The solution allows user to define the watermark text or image, position, color and font size to enrich their documents. The watermark can be easily customized and tailored to your needs. It can be pasted over any section and across any angle alignment throughout the page.
